results.name: E.g.f.: exp(x^2 * (exp(x) - 1)).
link: Vincenzo Librandi, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..200
Vaclav Kotesovec, Asymptotic solution of the equations using the Lambert W-function
formula: a(n) ~ exp((n-r^3)/(2+r)-n) * n^(n+1/2) / (r^n * sqrt((2*r^3*(3+r) + n*(1+r)*(4+r))/(2+r))), where r is the root of the equation r^2*((2+r) * exp(r) - 2) = n.
